<html>

<body>

<p>每个表格由 table 标签开始。</p>
<p>每个表格行由 tr 标签开始。</p>
<p>每个表格数据由 td 标签开始。</p>

<h4>一列：</h4>
<table border="1">
<tr>
  <td>100</td>
</tr>
</table>

<h4>一行三列：</h4>
<table border="1">
<tr>
  <td>100</td>
  <td>200</td>
  <td>300</td>
</tr>
</table>

<h4>两行三列：</h4>
<table border="1">
<tr>
  <td>100</td>
  <td>200</td>
  <td>300</td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td>400</td>
  <td>500</td>
  <td>600</td>
</tr>
</table>

<table	border="1">
<tr>
	<td>1</td>
    <td>1</td>
    <td>1</td>
    <td>1</td>
</tr>
<br/>
<br/>
<tr>
	<td>1</td>
    <td>1</td>
    <td>1</td>
    <td>1</td>
</tr>
</table>


</body>
</html>
每个表格由 table 标签开始。

每个表格行由 tr 标签开始。

每个表格数据由 td 标签开始。

border调节边框粗细

caption可以制作表格标题

colspan="2"跨列/将一行分为两列
rowspan="2"跨行/将一列分为两行 //放在表格<th><td>

cellpadding="50" 单元格边距
cellspacing="20" 单元格间距  //放在table中

align="left"
align="right"表格内同靠左/右


<html>

<body>

<h4>一个无序列表：</h4>
<ul>/<ol>
  <li>咖啡</li> //<ul>  <li>可以制作嵌套列表
  <li>茶</li>
  <li>牛奶</li>
</ul>/</ol> //ol中添加start="49"开始排序，若不添加数字默认从"1"开始

</body>
</html>


<html>
<head>
<style>
.cities { //先定义块的元素
    background-color:pink;
    color:white;
    margin:30px;
    padding:20px;
}	
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="cities">//引用块
<h2>London</h2>

<p>London is the capital city of England. It is the most populous city in the United Kingdom,
with a metropolitan area of over 13 million inhabitants.</p>

<p>Standing on the River Thames, London has been a major settlement for two millennia, 
its history going back to its founding by the Romans, who named it Londinium.</p>
</div> 

</body>
</html>
